cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with automatic medical image interpretation, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses machine learning (ML) models, which fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for report generation, which is a sub-field of NLP, hence cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
